<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٣٢٨⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(عبد اللَّه)</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span> بن <span class="c2">(عمر)</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span> في رجل نذر أن يزم أنفه قال: يكفر <span class="c2">(عن)</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span> يمينه <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
